653
00:42:20,940 --> 00:42:22,283
And look at him, wretch.

654
00:42:22,541 --> 00:42:23,747
Don't call him wretch.

655
00:42:23,943 --> 00:42:25,286
Why not?

656
00:42:25,377 --> 00:42:29,450
