Your Bareilly Ki Barfi.

663
00:42:41,994 --> 00:42:43,940
Here.
Groundnuts.

664
00:42:44,363 --> 00:42:46,365
Thank you.
Bless you.

665
00:42:53,072 --> 00:42:54,107
