709
00:45:16,682 --> 00:45:18,218
In Lucknow.

710
00:45:18,450 --> 00:45:19,895
Patrakarpuram.

711
00:45:19,952 --> 00:45:21,898
Thank you.
Have some cashews, son.

712
00:45:22,120 --> 00:45:23,064
Take it.

713
00:45:23,122 --> 00:45:25,830
