<i>Believe it or not,
we're crazy about you...</i>

1913
01:52:36,117 --> 01:52:40,031
<i>Listen o sweetheart,
we're your beloved.</i>

1914
01:52:54,836 --> 01:52:58,443
<i>Abracadabra...
my beloved's so handsome.</i>

1915
01:52:58,506 --> 01:53:02,113
<i>Always dressed smartly,
whether it's Delhi or Agra.</i>

